timelineManager.model

Class TimelineModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • timelineManager.model.TimelineModel

  • public class TimelineModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds an ArrayList of Timelines. It also has variables and methods that is needed for the Timeline Manager that is relevant to the model.
